@startuml
title Map Generation and Promotion

actor Operator
participant Frontend
participant "Control Plane API" as API
participant "Map Orchestrator" as Orchestrator
participant "Job Runtime" as Jobs
participant Mapper
database "Metadata Store" as Metadata
database "Media Store" as Media

Operator -> Frontend: Generate map
Frontend -> API: POST /maps/generate
API -> Orchestrator: create MapJob
Orchestrator -> Metadata: store queued job
API --> Frontend: 202 Accepted + jobId

loop Poll status
  Frontend -> API: GET /maps/jobs/:jobId
  API -> Metadata: read job state
  API --> Frontend: Job state
end

Orchestrator -> Jobs: execute MapJob
Jobs -> Metadata: load camera topology + observations + manual hints
Jobs -> Mapper: submit normalized map request
Mapper -> Mapper: Choose Plan A, B, or C internally
Mapper --> Jobs: MapResult
Jobs -> Orchestrator: validated result candidate
Orchestrator -> Metadata: store MapVersion and job completion
Orchestrator -> Media: write immutable map export
opt Promote after success
  Orchestrator -> Metadata: update active map pointer
end

Frontend -> API: GET /maps/latest
API -> Metadata: read active MapVersion
API --> Frontend: Active map

@enduml
